text: Hafiz Hafeezur Rehman (; born 1st January 1969) is a Pakistani politician. He is the 2nd Chief Minister of Gilgit-Baltistan and also leader of Pakistan's conservative political party PML-N, in Gilgit-Baltistan. He is serving in office since 2015. == References == Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani politicians Category:People from Gilgit-Baltistan
